<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It would be useful to be able to inject the ServiceManager into a Route - thus allowing, say, a URL to be checked against a users account via an Account Service.</p>

<p>Failing this, functionality to pull a Route out of the RouteStack, i.e. $sm-&gt;get('Router')-&gt;getRoute('routename');</p>

<p>Functionality only exists to add a route at present.</p>

